{"tid":835612,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"分享小小西班牙旅遊資料","createTime":"2018-09-25T04:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T05:17:56.000Z","uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"47c0b0f84b9164c597da210252890c44f471b7cf","tid":835612,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"2017年係鴨記買左張電話卡去西班牙，一去到睇SPEED就咁樣，之後都無咩變過，多數都只係用到係google map，反而同行個位就係當地出張卡就收4G... 而家睇返，寧願比自由鳥好過<br />\n<br />\n利申：非自由鳥打手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/125311_ab072c1e504b5ed33a5a38d4e010c256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F125311_ab072c1e504b5ed33a5a38d4e010c256.jpg&h=ac855c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/125312_763265269b6e61c6416aa549b5897c38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F125312_763265269b6e61c6416aa549b5897c38.jpg&h=302999c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e27c74564a27a2943abdc9f3b16ca2ead67bb6f2","tid":835612,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9a341d97a857f144d2c5343f69d201397aca850","tid":835612,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"如果有需要睇完古城Granada後，由市中心去機場，可以睇下個時間表 (2017)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/125825_e2843e4ceaf2d79cbf613d28c48e873f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F125825_e2843e4ceaf2d79cbf613d28c48e873f.jpg&h=3806bfcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b02f196534fca2c00873b0a7ec00c28c7e91cba0","tid":835612,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"如果想買火腿做手信，又唔係成隻腿囉返黎，可以買依個 ENRIQUE TOMAS（當地大集團，好易係街見到） package，簡單講佢係將成隻腳分好，再真空包裝，返黎自已慢慢食或派手信都好啱，價錢有平有貴，睇你買咩豬同月份，我就係巴塞買走，留意返，佢唔係間間店都有依個package，無就去另一間望下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/130020_adcf84db6ea48217c055806e79c9b4bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F130020_adcf84db6ea48217c055806e79c9b4bf.jpg&h=4f880cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/130020_2c116aa538d6c0f620a0865c27d465fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F130020_2c116aa538d6c0f620a0865c27d465fe.jpg&h=7f30b4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個樣係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enriquetomas.com/uk/158-medium_default/xsliced-pack-bellota-iberico-ham-shoulder.jpg.pagespeed.ic.7hAT-pcBP6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enriquetomas.com%2Fuk%2F158-medium_default%2Fxsliced-pack-bellota-iberico-ham-shoulder.jpg.pagespeed.ic.7hAT-pcBP6.jpg&h=8621d912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTravel Pack - Iberico Bellota Ham Shoulder<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.enriquetomas.com/uk/iberico-bellota-ham-shoulder/sliced-pack-bellota-iberico-ham-shoulder.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enriquetomas.com%2Fuk%2Fiberico-bellota-ham-shoulder%2Fsliced-pack-bellota-iberico-ham-shoulder.html&d=PKPzUjc7AK%2BMXcOldEzdc%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=340d5eb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.enriquetomas.com/uk/iberico-bellota-ham-shoulder/sliced-pack-bellota-iberico-ham-shoulder.html</a>"},{"pid":"4abf8283e67d0c153ccad4b1da146606668b1ba9","tid":835612,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"如果你想去睇皇馬主場賽事，去之前睇又要試網買飛或去到當地買黃牛？<br />\n<br />\n我個日去馬德里，係開波前一小時，去到班拿貝球場出面，就可以排隊買官方飛，排緊或未行到去，會有好多黃牛問你，個價多數都貴少少，但其實最緊要係唔係連位，我最後係官方櫃台買波飛，最貴係150歐/張，但無雙連位，我就買140歐/張，入場後就係中間最正中個位，150歐就坐我前一行。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當日睇皇馬對馬拉加，有8-9成入座</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/131115_f09903663d81ab2a6b13cefe924704c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F131115_f09903663d81ab2a6b13cefe924704c5.jpg&h=8ba1803d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/131116_b42c2e2b75c9900b0eb04876918a0c84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F131116_b42c2e2b75c9900b0eb04876918a0c84.jpg&h=13b9ed3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完!"}]}